OL,3,CLong-term social care reform unlikely
OL,4,Cbefore 2028, government says
OL,6,FCare workers will also be trained to
OL,7,Fperform health checks for patients in
OL,8,Fthe home to relieve pressure on the
OL,9,FNHS.
OL,11,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has now
OL,12,Fannounced an independent commission,
OL,13,Fled by Baroness Louise Casey, will
OL,14,Fbegin in April.
OL,16,FHe said: "In the first six months of
OL,17,Fthis government, work has already
OL,18,Fbegun on stabilising the care sector,
OL,19,Finvesting in prevention, and in carers
OL,20,Fand care workers.
