OL,4,Cbefore 2028, government says
OL,6,FThe commission will be split over two
OL,7,Fphases with the first, reporting to
OL,8,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer in mid-
OL,9,F2026, looking at the issues facing
OL,10,Fsocial care and recommending medium-
OL,11,Fterm reforms.
OL,13,FThe second phase is expected by 2028
OL,14,Fand will make recommendations for the
OL,15,Flonger term.
