OL,3,CLong-term social care reform unlikely
OL,4,Cbefore 2028, government says
OL,6,F"The current timetable to report by
OL,7,F2028 is far too long to wait for
OL,8,Fpeople who need social care, and their
OL,9,Ffamilies."
OL,11,FProfessor Martin Green, chief
OL,12,Fexecutive of Care England, said: "This
OL,13,Fannouncement acknowledges the decade-
OL,14,Flong crisis in social care, but it
OL,15,Frisks becoming yet another report that
OL,16,Fgathers dust while the sector crumbles.
OL,18,F"This commission will simply confirm
OL,19,Fwhat we already know ` how many more
OL,20,Freports must we endure before action
OL,21,Fis taken?"
